{"id":376675,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":15}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会<BR>","column":"","genre":"","count":"851","ytitle":"","mtitle":"战士的诗","ftitle":"","authors":["偰怀铎","刘聪玲","吴德如"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的炮群怒吼了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的炮群怒吼了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万雷齐鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地塌天崩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金门——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地都在发抖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金门——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陷入硝烟火海之中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直打得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匪徒们狼嚎鬼哭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直打得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国顾问胆战心惊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直打得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匪炮再也抬不起头；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直打得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匪机再也起不了身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的炮群怒吼了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听!这震动世界的声音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金门在发抖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾在发抖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直打得:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石抱着秃头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虚汗淋淋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾克——象发了瘧疾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在记者会上吐词不清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强盗们——你听:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是六亿人民的怒吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是解放台湾的先声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金门——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投降吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已陷入了绝境:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空已被我们封锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海面上也尽是我们的舰艇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你现在是:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“内无粮草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外无救兵”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要迷信你那“坚固”的工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一江山就是你很好的教训。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投降!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投降!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投降才能死里得生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注)过去蒋匪军在一江山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岛构筑了坚固的钢筋水泥的工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事，自以为不可被摧毁，但在我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强力的冲击下，几小时就被全部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摧毁了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(偰怀铎)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心在燃烧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心象万吨汽油被点燃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒火冲天不可遏止；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦亮我的武器:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀出鞘，跨战马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但等一声令下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随千军万马跃海齐驱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取第一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将五星红旗插在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的宝岛——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾的土地!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(刘聪玲)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗急跳墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗急要跳墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义急了要发狂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命战士齐警惕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳墙发狂可预防。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(吴德如)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年战士志气昂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年战士志气昂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象东方出太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积极练兵劲头大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随时准备打野狼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(徐光友)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民子弟兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民子弟兵，牢牢记在心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗是英雄，生产是尖兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒着暴风雨，抢稻如抢金。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金如山积，军民齐欢心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(张极)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜墙铁璧敌害怕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战备工作做到家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜墙铁壁敌害怕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假如他敢冒险来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫他个个回老家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(王志龙)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通讯兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢通讯兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口中带命令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸前藏封信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿山又越岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过万条河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面封锁线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匍匐在地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕子弹密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急速向前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军装撕破了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上留血印。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸手摸胸前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴胸一封信。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信象一团火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧热他的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛苦全忘尽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢通讯兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利回军营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都称赞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象只小雄鹰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(邢成飞)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兔子富来耗儿兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门大炮瞄金门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金门蒋帮寒了心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每逢太阳一落土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立刻打起探照灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"探照灯，探照灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺着海面扫不停，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯儿扫，心儿惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是群——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兔子官来耗子兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(于庆义)"}]}